==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Obsoleteness
<hw>Ob"so*lete*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state of
being obsolete, or no longer used; a state of desuetude.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>Indistinctness; want of
development.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Obsoletism</ent>⟦br⟧
